author: mrglavas
msg: JIRA Issue #1380: http://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/XERCESJ-1380. Eliminate redundant implementations of getData() and setData() from ProcessingInstructionImpl which are identical to the implementation of those methods in the parent class (CharacterDataImpl). Patch for removing getData() thanks to Ludger Bünger. I added the removal of setData().
